  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 879747072
    m_Localized: Sample content canonical root is empty. The normal playable path
      only accepts the Resources canonical root, and any editor filesystem fallback
      is restricted to diagnostic/internal lanes. Run SM/Internal/Content/Ensure
      Sample Content first, and use SM/Internal/Content/Generate Sample Content only
      as a repair path before entering Play mode.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 955244544
    m_Localized: Required sample content canonical root is empty, so boot cannot
      continue. The normal playable path only accepts the Resources content contract.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 955244545
    m_Localized: GameSessionRoot is missing.
